Penta Capital to Underwrite Broughton’s Tote Bid, Times Reports

-- B y   M i c h e l l e   E .   F r a z e r
-- 
2011-02-13T12:35:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-13/penta-capital-to-underwrite-broughton-s-tote-bid-times-reports.html
Penta Capital Partners Ltd. will
underwrite  Martin Broughton ’s bid for U.K. state-owned bookmaker
the Tote, the Sunday Times reported, without saying where it got
the information.  Broughton, deputy chairman of International Consolidated
Airlines Group SA, is one of a number of bidders for the betting
firm, the newspaper said. Other potential buyers include Betfred
Ltd., Gala Coral Group Ltd., the Reuben brothers and Tote’s
management, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Michelle E. Frazer in London at 
 mfrazer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net  